0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T13:24:13.000Z","msg":"如此看來，劇集帶着大陸的好口碑開播並不是壞事，起碼令人提起耐心看下去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d7EAQ6K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd7EAQ6K.png&h=0754dbd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n遲到好過無到，事隔一個半月，在大陸獲超過三萬文青追捧、八點九的豆瓣高分劇《歎息橋》凱旋而歸，回到娘家ViuTV見香港鄉親父老。集合了《綠豆》主角林保怡和周家怡，加入唱而優則演的陳奐仁和衛詩雅，圍繞四大主角還有他們的前度和家人，形成錯綜複雜的人物關係。撇開編劇刻意碎片化的淡淡然敘事方式，首周故事其實十分「葉念琛」，女人們因為寂寞一腳踏兩船，男人甜言蜜語後其實自私，簡直就是旺角活地亞倫的都市現代愛情殘酷物語。然而，當這一切加上伊底帕斯式戀母情結，就增加了內涵和文學性，<span style=\"color: gold;\">更重要是呈現手法看起來比較高級。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96abc7e5dca9ca44b1d9ccf6ae9e56d42ac35e0a","tid":2041838,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T13:31:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8d80897af9f486cbf6a410bcb08272b15b19c15","tid":2041838,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T14:14:54.000Z","msg":"連續三集冇主題曲想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ff7d1967c847db5e2dc6ebed3657fa384ef7418","tid":2041838,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T14:27:51.000Z","msg":"逆權司機唔敢播<br />\n激戰又唔敢播<br />\n播閨蜜二<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd695dcdf9cee30b44111abe15f6b71b57b93585","tid":2041838,"uid":248834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T15:04:42.000Z","msg":"點解冇人應你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f701b7bcac256579975455eac52c6d1591e28eff","tid":2041838,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd695dcdf9cee30b44111abe15f6b71b57b93585","tid":2041838,"uid":248834,"like":0,"